<%- include('partials/header')%>
<div class="relative w-full h-[400px]">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488521787991-ed7bbaae773c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1600"
    class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    alt="Hero"
  />
  <div class="absolute bottom-12 left-0 bg-red-primary text-white px-8 py-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold italic tracking-tight uppercase">
      CREATING IRREVERSIBLE POSITIVE CHANGE WITH AND FOR CHILDREN
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">
  <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-8 uppercase flex items-center space-x-2">
    <i class="fas fa-home"></i> <span>/ Overview</span>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-primary mb-8 tracking-wide">
      Bridge of Hopes OVERVIEW
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Bridge of Hopes is a non-profit organization dedicated to connecting
      compassion with action. We work to bridge the gap between opportunity and
      underprivileged lives — empowering communities through education, health,
      gender equality, and sustainable development. We believe that hope is not
      just a feeling — it’s a bridge that transforms dreams into reality. Our
      mission is to create pathways where every individual, regardless of their
      background, can walk towards dignity, empowerment, and a brighter future.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-10">
  <div
    class="bg-[#d7c4eb] flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-12 text-center min-h-[350px]"
  >
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
      To create an inclusive world where every human being has equal access to
      education, healthcare, and opportunities for growth — a world where
      compassion leads change and hope becomes strength.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative min-h-[350px] overflow-hidden bg-gray-200">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503454537195-1dcabb73ffb9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
      alt="Smiling Boy"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply opacity-80"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 grid grid-cols-4 grid-rows-4 pointer-events-none"
    >
      <div class="bg-[#d7c4eb]/30 border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="bg-[#d7c4eb]/30 border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative min-h-[350px] overflow-hidden bg-gray-200 order-last md:order-none"
  >
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488521787991-ed7bbaae773c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
      alt="Girl with Stethoscope"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply opacity-80"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 grid grid-cols-4 grid-rows-4 pointer-events-none"
    >
      <div class="bg-[#f2a2ab]/30 border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="bg-[#f2a2ab]/30 border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
      <div class="border-[0.5px] border-white/20"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="bg-[#f2a2ab] flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-12 text-center min-h-[350px]"
  >
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
   <ul class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-full  list-disc space-y-2">
  <li>
    To uplift underprivileged communities through education, health, and livelihood programs.
  </li>
  <li>
    To empower women and youth with skill development and leadership initiatives.
  </li>
  <li>
    To promote sustainable and environment-friendly practices that ensure a better tomorrow.
  </li>
  <li>
    To build a network of compassionate changemakers who stand together to create lasting impact.
  </li>
</ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20 ">
  <h2 class="text-center text-xl font-bold text-red-primary mb-4">
    OUR THEORY OF CHANGE
  </h2>
  <p
    class="text-center text-[10px] text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 uppercase tracking-tighter"
  >
    HOW WE BELIEVE THAT CHANGE HAPPENS FOR CHILDREN AND HOW WE CONTRIBUTE TO
    THAT CHANGE THROUGH OUR CORE FUNCTIONS AND OUR WORK IN PROGRAMS AND POLICY
    ADVOCACY.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
    <div
      class="bg-amber-500 text-white p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[280px]"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-trophy text-4xl mb-6"></i>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-sm leading-tight mb-4">
        INNOVATE AND DELIVER IMPACT AT SCALE
      </h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] leading-snug">
        To address the root causes of the challenges children face through
        programs that demonstrate impact.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-orange-600 text-white p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[280px]"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-hands-helping text-4xl mb-6"></i>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-sm leading-tight mb-4">
        BUILD COALITIONS AND PARTNERSHIPS
      </h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] leading-snug">
        Collaborating with local partners, civil society, and the government to
        ensure sustainable impact.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-[#4db848] text-white p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[280px]"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-bullhorn text-4xl mb-6"></i>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-sm leading-tight mb-4">
        BE A LOUD VOICE FOR CHILDREN
      </h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] leading-snug">
        Using our evidence-based programs to influence policy and ensure the
        rights of children are met.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-purple-500 text-white p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[280px]"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-4xl mb-6"></i>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-sm leading-tight mb-4">BE THE BEST INVESTOR</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] leading-snug">
        Ensuring that every rupee we receive is used efficiently to make a
        difference in children's lives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
  <h2 class="text-center text-xl font-bold text-red-primary mb-12">
    OUR JOURNEY IN THE LAST 15 YEARS
  </h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <div class="relative h-[300px]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503919545889-aef636e10ad4?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span
          class="bg-white px-8 py-2 font-bold text-xs tracking-widest shadow-lg"
          >EDUCATION</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative h-[300px]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484662020986-75935d2ebc66?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span
          class="bg-white px-8 py-2 font-bold text-xs tracking-widest shadow-lg"
          >CHILD PROTECTION</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative h-[300px]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532938911079-1b06ac7ceec7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span
          class="bg-white px-8 py-2 font-bold text-xs tracking-widest shadow-lg uppercase"
          >Health & Nutrition</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative h-[300px]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511632765486-a01980e01a18?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span
          class="bg-white px-8 py-2 font-bold text-xs tracking-widest shadow-lg uppercase"
          >Poverty & Inclusion</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
 



<%- include('partials/footer') %>
